# Delay Poison
[[DNDSRD/35eSRD/Definicoes/Magic Descriptions/Conjuration|Conjuration]] ([[DNDSRD/35eSRD/Combat/HEALING|healing]])  <s class="aside-hide">![Delay Poison.png](data:image/png;base64,)</s>
**Level**:: Bard2 Cleric2 Druid2 Paladin2 Ranger1 
**Components**:: V S DF 
**CastingTime**:: 1 standard 
**Range**:: [[touch|touch]]
**Target**:: creature touched
**Area**:: 
**Duration**:: 1 hour/level
**SavingThrow**:: Fortitude negates (harmless)
**SpellResistance**:: true

**snip**:: Stopspoisonfrom harming subject for 1 hour/ level. ^onelinedescription




The subject becomes temporarily immune to poison. Any poison in its system or any poison to which it is exposed during the spells duration does not affect the subject until the spells duration has expired. *Delay poison *does not cure any damage that poison may have already done.
